  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You learn to utilize the hive mind integrity of your insects to cast and maintain Ninjutsu, you gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Increase your Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You reduce the cost to maintain Aburame clan jutsu by an amount equal to its rank. (D-Rank: 1, C-Rank: 2, B-Rank: 3, A-Rank: 4, S-Rank: 5)</p></li><li><p>You learn one additional Aburame clan jutsu that you qualify for.</p></li><li><p>You can learn and create Aburame clan jutsu in half the time.</p></li></ul>",
